reviews: I got this bra in the summer and have only worn it three times. When I washed it the third time the plastic part actually broke during the hand wash cycle. Now I cannot wear it and it was a true waste of money since the return window closed a month after I got it. Save your money and by a better constructed bra. If you’re willing to hand wash it every time you may be ok!
